awn of our love will be as powerful and transformative as the rise of the Olympians.</div><div><br></div><div>Our story will be one of creation, of building a life together filled with love, understanding, and shared dreams. I envision us as modern Olympians, creating our own world where love and harmony reign supreme.</div><div><br></div><div>My dear Ivory, may this story of creation and divine order remind us of the power of new beginnings and the beauty of love that transforms. I will continue to seek you with the determination of Zeus and the hope of a new dawn.</div><div><br></div><div>With all my love,</div><div><br></div><div>Wendell</div>
